article_title: Newly eligible Medicaid members can choose from Anthem, Humana or Passport
article_text: The state has signed contracts with three Medicaid managed care companies to serve Kentuckians who will be newly eligible for Medicaid under the federal Affordable Care Act, officials said Friday.
